- You may have three (3) characters.
- PKers may kill PKs and that's the only PK allowed outside of arenas.
- Do not abuse bugs, steal, spam, harass or in any way ruin the game for
    other players.
- Shopkeepers are not tanks or mortal retirement funds.
- Keep your language and actions clean in public places and on public channels.
- Do not hoard eq. or keys or use another clan's items (ransoming okay).
    Respect others and have FUN!
